      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required for MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 scoping.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error beyond discretization and code verification is not required to be separately assessed at MRL 2. The factor is acknowledged but scoped out consistent with the model risk level determination."
